OL,3,CAlmost one in 10 believe they may have
OL,4,Clong Covid, research finds
OL,6,FLong Covid is a chronic condition
OL,7,Finduced by Covid-19 infection, with
OL,8,Fsymptoms including fatigue, feeling
OL,9,Fshort of breath, 'brain fog', and
OL,10,Fheart palpitations.
OL,12,FThe findings, which show 9.1% believe
OL,13,Fthey may have long Covid, are part of
OL,14,Fthe study published in the journal
OL,15,FHealth Expectations.
OL,17,FProfessor Nisreen Alwan said: "This
OL,18,Fanalysis adds further evidence of the
OL,19,Funfairness of long Covid, with people
OL,20,Fwho are already disadvantaged in
OL,21,Fsociety more likely to be affected.
