OL,3,CAlmost one in 10 believe they may have
OL,4,Clong Covid, research finds
OL,6,F"It also shows us that many people
OL,7,Faren't sure if they have it, and may
OL,8,Fneed diagnosis, treatment and support.
OL,10,F"Long Covid is still a very
OL,11,Fsignificant issue impacting
OL,12,Findividuals, families, the economy and
OL,13,Fwider society. We need to do more to
OL,14,Fprevent it, diagnose it, and properly
OL,15,Fsupport people who are affected by it."
